Masu zanga-zanga sun fito kan tituna a birane da yawa a Amirka don su jawo hankali ga rashin adalci na launin fata.
Taron zanga-zanga a Portland, Oregon, ya kasance na tsawon watanni biyu, tun bayan mutuwar George Floyd a ranar 25 ga Mayu yayin da yake tsare da 'yan sanda a Minneapolis, Minnesota.
Gwamnatin Trump ta aika da jami'an tarayya zuwa Portland, suna ƙara ƙarin man fetur ga zanga-zangar.
Masu zanga-zangar yanzu suna zanga-zangar nuna rashin amincewar tarayya a birnin.
A Seattle, 'yan sanda sun yi amfani da fashewar wuta da gas mai zubar da hawaye sun kama mutane 45 a ranar Asabar bayan zanga-zangar goyon baya ko kuma zanga-zangar da ta faru a Portland ta zama mai tashin hankali.
'Yan sanda sun ce jami'an 'yan sanda fiye da 20 sun ji rauni.
A daren Asabar, a birnin Austin, Texas, an kashe wani mutum lokacin da aka harbe shi a wani gangamin 'Yan Tafiya na Black Lives Matter.
Rahotanni na kafofin watsa labarai sun ce mutumin ya iya kusantar da wata mota tare da bindiga kafin a harbe shi.
"Duk abin da na sani shi ne cewa mutuwa yayin zanga-zangar abu ne mai ban tsoro", in ji magajin garin Steve Adler na Austin a wata sanarwa.
Adler ya ce yana "karyayye kuma ya yi mamaki".
A birnin Louisville, Kentucky, wasu 'yan zanga-zangar da suke dauke da makamai sun yi kira ga a yi wa Breonna Taylor adalci, wata mata 'yar Baƙar fata da ta mutu a birnin Louisville lokacin da 'yan sanda suka shiga gidanta ba tare da an ba ta umurni ba kuma suka harbe ta.
Abokin saurayin Taylor ya fara harbi 'yan sanda, yana tunanin su masu shiga cikin gida ne.
An kori wani jami'in 'yan sanda saboda lamarin Taylor, amma ba a shigar da tuhuma a kan sauran jami'an ba.
Shugaban kungiyar NFAC, wani mayakan 'yan bakar fata da ke da hannu a zanga-zangar, ya ce yana son binciken 'yan sanda a kan kisan Taylor ya zama mafi gaskiya.
