An bayyana dalilin hatsarin jirgin saman da aka kai mataimakin shugaban kasa Yemi Osinbajo a Kabba, jihar Kogi.
Jirgin ya fadi a ranar 2 ga Fabrairu a Kabba, dauke da Osinbajo da mataimakansa takwas.
Shugaban hukumar binciken hatsarin kasa, Akin Olateru, ya ce matukin jirgin ya yi amfani da hanyar saukowa da ba daidai ba.
Ya kuma ce direban bai bi dokokin saukar da jirgi ba ko kuma dokokin jirgi da kamfanin jirgin ya kafa.
Jirgin saman, AW 139, wanda Agusta Westland ya yi, ya sauka a filin wasan ƙwallon ƙafa.
Mai matukin jirgi na jirgin ya isa Kabba a yanayin yanayi mai duhu kuma bai iya gani sosai ba.
Sa'ad da yake gab da sauka, sai ya nufi filin ƙwallon ƙafa, tsakanin shi da filin wasa don sauka na gaggawa.
Bayan ya yi karo da ƙasa, sai ya ja da baya kuma ya daina bayan ya fāɗi a gefensa na dama.
Amma a kan mataimakin Buhari da abokan tafiyarsa takwas, babu wanda ya ji rauni.
Daga cikin wadanda ke cikin jirgin tare da Osinbajo, akwai mai ba Buhari shawara kan harkokin siyasa, Babafemi Ujudu.
Gidan baje kolin shigo da kayayyaki na kasar Sin (CIIE) ya nuna karfin kasar Sin wajen aiwatar da manufofin ci gaba.
Duk wani mai bin kafofin watsa labarai na yada labarai ba zai rasa ganin yadda ake bude baje kolin kayayyakin da ake shigo da su kasar Sin ba ko kuma baje kolin shigo da kayayyaki na kasa da kasa na kasar Sin na uku (CIIE) a birnin Shanghai.
Idan muka kalli jawabin shugaban kasar Sin Xi Jinping a lokacin bikin bude baje kolin, za mu ga yadda ya bayyana sabbin matakai da kasarsa za ta dauka dangane da budewa ga kasashen waje a duk fannonin kasuwanci, a mataki na "Ku yi aiki tare ku tsira tare".
Baya ga budewa, akwai wasu muhimman shawarwari na ci gaba wanda hukumomin kasar Sin suka tsara aiwatar da su, ciki har da ci gaba da inganta yanayin zuba jari na kasashen waje na kasar, cinikin sabis na duniya, da kuma ci gaban tattalin arziki ta hanyar fasahar yanar gizo ta zamani, canje-canje masu yawa, kirkire-kirkire a cikin kasuwanci da zuba jari, da kuma cinikin kasuwa, da dai sauransu.
Idan muka duba sosai, wannan ba zai je baje kolin CIIE ba, zai ba da dama ga dukan duniya ta tabbatar da cewa manufofin ci gaban tattalin arzikin kasar Sin ba za su canza ba.
Kuma ƙalubalen da ke ƙaruwa da China da sauran sassan duniya ke fuskanta tare a yaƙi da COVID-19 ba zai sa China ta dakatar da tsare-tsaren ci gabanta ba.
A gaskiya ma, mun ga yadda baje kolin na wannan shekara ya jawo hankalin karin mahalarta daga kamfanoni, masana'antu, "masu kasuwanci da wakilan gwamnati, ciki har da daga Afirka, wadanda suka yaba wa kokarin da kasar Sin ta yi na rungumar al'ummar duniya a kokarin da ta yi na cimma nasara tare.
A takaice, za mu iya cewa nasarar da kasar Sin ta samu wajen dakile COVID-19, kokarin da ta yi na tabbatar da ci gaban tattalin arzikin cikin gida, da kuma kokarin da ta yi na bude kofofinta ga kasashen waje, da kuma gudanar da baje kolin CIIE a wannan lokacin da duniya ke fuskantar babban kalubale, alama ce da ke tabbatar da karfinta na ci gaba da aiwatar da burin bunkasa ta kamar yadda aka tsara.
Dogara ya gana da Buhari bayan ya koma APC.
Tsohon shugaban majalisar wakilai a Najeriya Yakubu Dogara ya koma jam'iyyar APC a lokacin ganawarsa da Shugaba Buhari a gidan shugaban kasa a Abuja.
Gwamnan jihar Yobe kuma shugaban majalisar wakilai na jam'iyyar All Progressives Congress (APC), Mai Mala Buni, ya tabbatar da gudun hijira a lokacin taron manema labarai a Abuja.
Buni ya ce bai kamata 'yan Najeriya su yi mamakin wannan gudun hijira ba domin tsohon shugaban majalisar wakilai dan jam'iyyar All Progressives Congress (APC) ne, kuma yanzu ya tattauna dalilin da ya sa ya bar jam'iyyar a baya.
A ranar 29 ga Janairu, 2019, Dogara ya sanar da cewa ya koma PDP.
Bayan ya koma PDP, Dogara ya lashe takarar sake zaɓe ga majalisar wakilai, inda mutanen mazabar Bogoro, Dassa da Tafabalewa a jihar Bauchi suka sake zaɓe shi.
Wilfried Zaha yana son barin Crystal Palace, Roy Hodgson ya ce: "Ka lura da wannan sararin samaniya"
Kocin Crystal Palace Roy Hodgson ya ba da bugun jini ga magoya baya kafin rufe kakar wasa ta hanyar bayyana cewa dan wasan da ya yi barazanar Wilf Zaha yana son barin kulob din.
Dan wasan na kasar Ivory Coast ya kasance a Selhurst Park sama da shekaru biyar kuma yanzu yana ganin zai bar, tun da ya kasance yana da alaƙa da 'yan wasa kamar Arsenal da Bayern Munich.
A shekara ta 27 ya rage a gani idan wannan rukunin kulob din har yanzu suna sha'awar yin babban kuɗi a kansa, musamman a wannan bazarar tare da rashin tabbas na tattalin arziki a cikin wasanni, bayan yakin neman zabe inda Zaha ya zira kwallaye hudu kuma ya yi rajistar taimako biyar don wani ɓangare na Palace wanda bai yi wahayi ba.
Da yake magana bayan wasan bayan ranar karshe, Hodgson ya gaya wa Alex Crook na TalkSport ya "yi la'akari da wannan sararin samaniya" game da yiwuwar fita ta Zaha bayan ya yarda cewa mai gaba ya "bayyana" cewa yana ganin makomar sa daga kulob din.
Har yanzu dan wasan yana da shekara uku a kan yarjejeniyar Palace da ya yi a shekarar da ta gabata kuma sun ce zai dauki fam miliyan 100 don ya bar kulob din.
Kungiyar Hodgson ta kammala yakin neman zabe da cin nasara bakwai a jere da kuma wasan karshe, inda ta fadi zuwa matsayi na 14 a cikin tsari.
Zaha da kansa ya zira kwallaye sau daya kawai tsakanin tsakiyar watan Disamba da ƙarshen kakar wasa, bugun doguwar nesa a cikin rashin nasara ga Chelsea.
An ruwaito cewa ya mika bukatar canja wurin a lokacin rani na baya a kokarin tilasta wani motsi, amma wani tayin bai samu don ya jarabci Palace ya sayar.
A wani mataki na ganin zai kara saukin sa, Zaha ya sauya jami'an a watan Janairu kuma a makonni masu zuwa zai fi dacewa ya samu damar yin hakan.
Zaha shi ne dan wasan da ya fi yawan minti a gasar Premier a wannan kakar Palace kuma shi ne dan wasan da ya fi shekaru 28 da haihuwa da ya buga minti 1,100 ko fiye, yana nuna matakin sake gina da za a buƙaci a cikin tawagar tare da yiwuwar kudaden da aka kawo don lambar 11.
Malaysia na neman 'yan Rohingya 24 da ake zargin sun mutu a tsibirin
KUALA LUMPUR, Malaysia (AP) - Hukumomin Malaysia sun ce a ranar Lahadi suna neman 'yan gudun hijirar Rohingya ashirin da biyu wadanda ake zargin sun nutse bayan sun tsallake daga jirgin su a tsibirin Langkawi da ke arewacin kasar.
Zawawi Abdullah, babban jami'in hukumar kula da ayyukan ruwa ta Malaysia, ya ce bayanan farko na 'yan sanda sun nuna cewa daya daga cikin mazaje 25 na Rohingya da suka tsalle daga jirgin sun yi nasarar yin iyo zuwa gabar tekun.
Wanda ya tsira ne kawai ya nemi taimakon 'yan sanda a daren Asabar kuma an tsare shi domin ci gaba da bincike, in ji Zawawi.
Daruruwan dubban Musulmi Rohingya sun tsere daga Myanmar saboda yunkurin da sojoji suka yi, kuma da yawa suna zaune a sansanonin 'yan gudun hijira da ke da yawan mutane a Bangladesh.
Kasar Malaysia da Musulmai ke mamaye ta kasance wuri na kowa ga jiragen ruwa da masu safarar mutane suka shirya da suka yi alkawarin samun rayuwa mafi kyau a kasashen waje.
Zawawi ya ce an tura jiragen ruwa biyu da jirgin sama a binciken.
Ya ce hukumar za ta kuma gargadi masuntan da hukumomin yankin da ke makwabtaka da Thailand don taimakawa wajen binciken.
Bai ba da ƙarin bayani game da jirgin ba.
A watan jiya, hukumomin Malaysia sun tsare 'yan gudun hijirar Rohingya 269 kuma sun gano gawarwaki a cikin wani jirgin ruwa da ake zargi da kutse a kusa da Langkawi wanda suka ce an lalata shi da gangan don haka ba za a iya mayar da shi cikin teku ba.
Daga baya Hukumar Kula da Kula da Tekun Malaysia ta ce an kwashe 269 daga wani jirgin ruwa mafi girma wanda ake ganin mutane da dama sun mutu kuma an jefa jikinsu cikin teku.
Firayim Minista Muhyiddin Yassin ya ce Malaysia ba za ta iya karɓar ƙarin 'yan gudun hijirar Rohingya ba yayin da take gwagwarmaya da jinkirin tattalin arziki saboda annobar coronavirus.
Amma ya ce wadanda suka riga sun kasance a kasar ba za a sake tura su zuwa teku ba.
Malaysia ta kasance gida ga 'yan gudun hijira ba bisa ka'ida ba fiye da miliyan biyu da kuma 'yan gudun hijira da masu neman mafaka kimanin 180,000 - ciki har da 'yan Rohingya 101,000 - waɗanda aka yi rajista a hukumar 'yan gudun hijira ta Majalisar Dinkin Duniya.
Amurka ta yi kokarin kulla alaka tsakanin Isra'ila da Hadaddiyar Daular Larabawa.
Gwamnatin Shugaba Trump za ta aika manyan jami'ai biyu zuwa Gabas ta Tsakiya a wannan makon, da nufin karfafa yarjejeniyar tarihi tsakanin Isra'ila da Hadaddiyar Daular Larabawa, don kafa alakar diflomasiyya.
Jami'an diflomasiyya uku sun ce Sakataren Harkokin Wajen Amurka Mike Pompeo tare da surukin shugaban kasar Donald Trump da babban mai ba da shawara, Jared Kushner, suna shirin ziyartar kasashe daban-daban a yankin a cikin 'yan kwanaki masu zuwa, domin karfafa sake kafa dangantakar tsakanin Daular da Isra'ila.
Ana sa ran Pompeo zai tashi a ranar Lahadi zuwa Isra'ila, Bahrain, Oman, Hadaddiyar Daular Larabawa, Qatar da Sudan, a cewar jami'an diflomasiyya wadanda suka nemi a boye sunansu saboda ba a kammala jadawalin tafiye-tafiye ba ko kuma a sanar da su ba.
A halin yanzu Kushner zai tashi a karshen mako zuwa Isra'ila, Bahrain, Oman, Saudiyya da Morocco.
Ana sa ran ziyararsu za ta kai ga sanarwar cimma matsaya bisa ga diflomasiyya, ko da yake dukansu suna da akalla manufa guda ɗaya, don daidaita sharuɗɗan yarjejeniyar da Isra'ila a nan gaba.
An kuma shirya Pompeo ya yi tattaunawa da kungiyar Taliban a Qatar kan batutuwan da suka shafi tattaunawar zaman lafiya, wanda zai zama muhimmin mataki wajen janye sauran sojojin Amurka daga Afghanistan.
Fadar White House da Ma'aikatar Harkokin Waje ba su yi sharhi ba game da ziyarar da ba za ta kasance wani ɓangare na ƙoƙarin gwamnatin Amurka na ƙarfafa alaƙa tsakanin Hadaddiyar Daular Larabawa da Isra'ila, ko da yake ba ta cimma sulhu a cikin gwagwarmayar tsakanin Isra'ila da Falasdinu ba.
