Hadarin ya faru ne a ranar Asabar da yamma lokacin da jirgin Piper PA-32 wanda ke dauke da mutane shida ya fadi a cikin wani lambu a birnin West Jordan, in ji mai magana da yawun Hukumar Kula da Sufurin Jiragen Sama ta Tarayya Allen Kenitzer.
Mutane uku a cikin jirgin sun mutu, ciki har da matukin jirgi, wanda 'yan sanda suka gano shi a matsayin Lee Wyckoff mai shekara 43, jaririnsa mai watanni 9, da Milda Shibonis, mai shekara 36, West Jordan 'yan sanda sun ce.
