Wata mace mai shekaru 72 da haihuwa da ke cikin gidan da jirgin ya buge tana cikin mawuyacin hali, a cewar wani sakon Twitter a ranar Lahadi daga sashen 'yan sanda.
Har ila yau, hatsarin ya lalata gidaje uku, in ji kakakin birnin West Jordan Tauni Barker.
