Za a tuna cewa, a ranar Lahadi da ta gabata dubban mutane sun yi maraba da tsohon Sarkin Kano Muhammadu Sanusi II a ziyarar da ya kai a gidan gwamnatin jihar.
A cewar rahoton, Sultan ya ziyarci Gwamna Nasiru El-rufa'i don tattauna tsaro a kudancin Kaduna.
Yankin kudancin Kaduna ya dade yana cike da tashin hankali tsakanin kabilu.
Yadda Za a Fara Hajji a Wannan Shekarar
Yawan mutanen da za su iya halartar aikin Hajji na wannan shekara an rage saboda yaduwar cutar coronavirus a duniya.
Maimakon fiye da miliyan biyu na masu aikin hajji da ke yin wannan aikin hajji na shekara-shekara daga ko'ina cikin duniya, hukumomin kasar sun iyakance aikin hajji na wannan shekara ga 'yan kasar Saudiyya 1,000 da kuma 'yan kasashen waje da ke zaune a kasar, mutanen da aka kimanta a cikin makonnin da suka gabata.
An gwada masu aikin hajji tsakanin shekaru 20 zuwa 50 don COVID-19 kafin su shiga Makka, inda aka buƙaci su ware kansu na makonni 2 a ɗakunan otal ɗin su, kafin su iya yin aikin hajji.
Musulmai a duk fadin duniya suna zuwa yin aikin Hajji domin cika daya daga cikin ginshiƙan Musulunci, wanda shine cewa ana buƙatar mutum ya yi aikin Hajji aƙalla sau ɗaya a rayuwarsa zuwa wannan wuri mafi tsarki ga mabiyan Musulunci.
Bayan da waɗanda suka je aikin hajji a wannan shekara suka kammala aikin hajji, an bukaci su ware kansu na mako guda don su tabbata cewa ba su kamu da cutar a lokacin aikin hajji ba.
Sachin Pilot vs Ashok Gehlot; BJP ta ce jihar tana cikin rikicin siyasa; Congress na son gwajin ƙasa
Ashok Gehlot ya ce idan ya cancanta, Majalisar za ta yi zanga-zanga a wajen gidan Firayim Minista.
Wata rana bayan ya jagoranci dharna a Raj Bhawan a Jaipur, Babban Ministan Rajasthan Ashok Gehlot a ranar Asabar ya ce idan ya cancanta, 'yan majalisar dokokin Congress za su gana da Shugaban kasa kuma su yi zanga-zanga a waje da fadar firaministan don magance rikicin jihar.
A wani taron jam'iyyar majalisa ta majalisa (CLP), Mista Gehlot ya nuna cewa shirin shine a yi gwajin ƙasa don tabbatar da cewa yawancin 'yan majalisa na majalisa da abokan tarayya suna tare da shi a gwagwarmayar mulki.
"Ya ce gwamnati tana da rinjaye kuma tana son zuwa majalisar", a cikin wata sanarwa da shugaban majalisa Mahesh Joshi ya fitar bayan taron CLP ya ce.
An gudanar da taron CLP a otal inda 'yan majalisar dokokin kasar da ke sansanin Gehlot ke tsare har tsawon kwanaki.
"Shugaban ministan ya gaya mana mu kasance a shirye mu zauna a otal ɗin na tsawon lokaci.
Ya ce idan ya cancanta, za mu je mu sadu da Shugaban kasa kuma za mu gudanar da dharna a wajen fadar Firayim Minista, "in ji wani shugaban jam'iyyar.
Gwamnan Rajasthan dole ne ya kira taron majalisar don bari Congress ta tabbatar da rinjayarta, shugaban jam'iyyar Rahul Gandhi ya ce a ranar Juma'a, yana zargin cewa makircin BJP na rushe gwamnatin Ashok Gehlot yanzu ya bayyana.
"Ana mulkin ƙasar bisa ga doka da kuma kundin tsarin mulki.
Ana kafa gwamnatoci kuma ana gudanar da su bisa ga umurnin mutane.
Shiryayyar BJP don rushe gwamnatin Rajasthan a fili ce.
Wannan zargi ne ga mutane miliyan takwas na Rajasthan.
Gwamnan dole ne ya kira taron majalisar domin gaskiyar ta zo gaban kasar", Mr Gandhi ya wallafa a shafinsa na Twitter a harshen Hindi.
Babban Ministan Rajasthan Ashok Gehlot ya shaida wa 'yan majalisar dokokin kasar a ranar Asabar cewa ya shirya zuwa wurin shugaban kasar Indiya don tabbatar da cewa abin da ya kira "takarar BJP" don dakatar da gwajin ƙarfi ba zai yi nasara ba.
Mista Gehlot, wanda ya yi zanga-zangar tsawon sa'o'i a gidan Gwamna Kalraj Mishra a ranar Juma'a don matsa lamba don zaman majalisar, ya yi taro da 'yan majalisar dokoki na Congress da majalisar ministocinsa a ranar Asabar, bayan haka an tsara sabon tsari kuma majalisar ta amince da shi.
A daren jiya Mr Mishra ya nemi Mr Gehlot ya sake gabatar da bukatar taron jama'a, yana mai da martani shida.
Za a aika wannan shawarar ga Gwamna nan ba da jimawa ba.
Mista Gehlot ya zargi Gwamnan da jinkirta zaman domin yana "a karkashin matsin lamba" don dakatar da gwajin ƙarfin gwamnatinsa.
Yayin da Mista Gehlot ya gana da majalisar ministocinsa, tawagar BJP karkashin jagorancin shugaban BJP na Rajasthan Satish Poonia da shugaban adawa Gulab Chandra Kataria sun gana da Gwamna don tattauna halin da ake ciki na COVID-19 a jihar.
Gudanar da CIIE a kasar Sin alama ce ta burinta na raba damar da take da ita da duniya.
Shugaban kasar Sin Xi Jinping ya ce shirya baje kolin shigo da fitar da kayayyaki na kasar Sin na uku (CIIE) alama ce ta babbar aniyar kasar Sin ta raba damar kasuwarta da sauran kasashen duniya, da kuma bayar da gudummawa wajen farfado da tattalin arzikin duniya.
Shi, wanda ya yi jawabi a lokacin bude baje kolin na wannan shekara, wanda aka bude a yammacin ranar Laraba ta hanyar bidiyo, ya ce yana da muhimmanci a nace a kan ka'idar ci gaba da harkokin duniya ta hanyar tattaunawa, da kuma kiyaye tsarin cinikayya na bangarori da yawa a karkashin jagorancin Hukumar Ciniki ta Duniya, domin ci gaba da gina tattalin arzikin cinikayya na duniya ba tare da rufewa ba.
Xi ya ci gaba da cewa kasar Sin ta gabatar da manufofin fadada hulda tsakanin kasuwannin cikin gida, da kuma fadada hulda tsakanin kasuwannin duniya, domin biyan bukatun cikin gida, da kuma bukatun al'umma ta duniya.
Xi ya kara da cewa kasar Sin na da yawan jama'a da suka kai biliyan 1.4, wanda yawan mutanen da ke samun kudin shiga na kimanin yuan 5,000 na kasar Sin a wata ya kai miliyan 400, wanda ya sa kasar Sin ta zama babbar kasuwar duniya, kuma ana ganin cewa a cikin shekaru goma masu zuwa, jimlar shigo da kayayyaki zuwa kasar za ta kai dala tiriliyan 22 na Amurka.
Shugaban kasar Sin Xi Jinping ya sanar da sabbin matakai da kasarsa za ta dauka wajen budewa a dukkan fannoni.
Shugaban ya yi wannan jawabin ne a jawabinsa a bikin bude bikin baje kolin shigo da fitar da kayayyaki na kasar Sin na kasa da kasa na 3 (CIIE) a birnin Shanghai.
Shugaban ya ce kasarsa za ta gabatar da jerin kayayyaki da za ta dakatar a fagen ayyukan kasuwanci na duniya, kuma za ta fadada wasu bangarori, kamar ci gaban tattalin arziki ta hanyar amfani da fasahar yanar gizo ta zamani, da zurfafa canji, kirkire-kirkire a kasuwanci da zuba jari, cinikayya ta kyauta, da kuma samar da yanayi mai kyau na kasuwanci.
Bugu da kari, a cewar Shugaba Xi Jinping, China za ta rage yawan fasahohin da aka haramta ko kuma aka hana shigo da su, domin samar da yanayi mai kyau don musayar fasahar zamani tsakanin al'ummai.
Bugu da kari, kasar Sin za ta ci gaba da inganta tsarin shari'arta, ta yadda za ta bi ka'idodin kasa da kasa a fannin budewa, nuna gaskiya, da karfafa kare hakkin mallakar ilimi, da kuma bukatun masu zuba jari na kasashen waje da kuma samar musu da kariya ta doka.
Ya ce kasar Sin ta shirya ta rattaba hannu kan yarjejeniyar cinikayya ta 'yanci don ci gaba da sauran kasashen duniya.
An faɗaɗa gwajin COVID-19 a Senegal
Senegal na fadada gwajin cutar coronavirus don ba matafiya damar yin gwaji kafin barin kasar, da kuma wadanda suka isa kasar ta yammacin Afirka, a cewar Reuters.
