Serbia na neman karin jiragen yaki a tsakiyar tashin hankali a yankin Balkan
Belgrade, Serbia (AP) - Serbia za ta karfafa rundunarta ta soja kuma tana neman sayen karin jiragen yaki a yayin da tashin hankali ke kara tsanani a yankin Balkan, shugaban kasar Serbia ya ce a ranar Lahadi.
Shugaba Aleksandar Vucic ya ce an yi "wasu shirye-shirye" don sayen jirgin saman fashewar bam, yana zargin Amurka da sauran kasashen yamma da sanya makamai ga makwabtan Serbia na NATO da tsohuwar lardin Kosovo.
"Amurkawa, Turkawa da Jamus suna kula da ɗansu ƙaunatacce", in ji Vucic, yana magana ne game da Kosovo.
Ya ce Amurka ta kawo wasu motocin sulke ga jami'an tsaro na Kosovo kwanan nan.
A lokacin da ya ziyarci rundunar sojojin sojojin Serbia, Vucic ya ce kasarsa ba za ta iya yin gasa da "bayarwar NATO" ga makwabta ba idan ya zo ga makamai, "saboda haka dole ne mu yi shi kadai".
Vucic bai bayyana irin jiragen yakin da Serbia ke shirin saya ba, amma kafofin yada labarai na gwamnati sun ce gwamnatinsa ta nemi Amurka ta ba da jiragen saman fashewa 20.
Rahotanni sun ce har yanzu Washington ba ta amsa bukatar Belgrade ba kuma idan aka ki, zai sayi jirgin saman kai hari na Sukhoi-25 na Rasha.
Serbia, wadda ta ce ba ta da tsaka tsaki a harkokin soji, kwanan nan ta karbi tsarin tsayayyen jirgin sama mai zurfi daga Rasha, wanda kuma ya ba da jiragen yaki, jiragen saman kai hari da motocin sulke.
Wani abokin tarayyar Serbia, China, ta kawo jiragen sama masu saukar ungulu na soja.
A baya jami'an Amurka sun yi magana a fili game da gabatar da takunkumi kan Serbia idan Moscow ta tura karin makamai zuwa kasar, musamman wadanda zasu iya kawo hadarin tsaro na kasashen makwabta na NATO.
Ana kallon makaman Rasha da Sin na Serbia da damuwa a Yammacin Turai da kuma tsakanin makwabtan Serbia.
Aikin da ake yi a yankin Balkans ya ci gaba da ƙaruwa, wanda ya yi fama da mummunan yakin basasa a shekarun 1990.
NATO ta shiga tsakani a Serbia don dakatar da zubar da jini na Serbs a kan Kosovo Albanian separatists a 1999.
Duk da neman shiga Tarayyar Turai, shugabancin Serbia na goyon bayan jama'a ya kara karfafa alakar siyasa da soja da Kremlin, da kuma Beijing.
Serbia, da Rasha da China, ba su yarda da 'yancin kai na Kosovo, wanda Amurka da yawancin Yammacin duniya suka amince da shi.
