Hurricane Hanna: Texas da ke fama da cutar Coronavirus ta fuskanci sabon barazanar ambaliyar ruwa a cikin 'mafi yawan'
Masu duba yanayi suna hasashen "ruwa mai ban tsoro" a kudancin Texas bayan Hurricane Hanna ya kai ga ƙasa sau biyu, yana kawo ruwan sama mai yawa da iska har zuwa 90 mph.
Ya sauka a ranar Asabar a matsayin guguwa ta farko (mafi ƙanƙanta daga cikin matakan biyar) kuma yanzu an rage shi zuwa guguwa mai zafi - amma har yanzu akwai iya samun ruwan sama 15-30 cm (6-12in) a ranar Lahadi tare da iska 60mph.
Wasu yankuna sun riga sun ba da rahoton samun ruwan sama har zuwa 23cm, ciki har da gundumar Cameron, wadda ke kan iyaka da Mexico.
Hanna ita ce farkon guguwar guguwar Atlantic ta 2020, kuma masanin yanayi Chris Birchfield ya gargadi mazauna su kasance a faɗake, yana cewa: "Ba mu ma kusa da ƙarshen a wannan lokacin ba. Har yanzu muna tsammanin ambaliyar bala'i".
Texas ta riga ta fuskanci karuwar yawan masu kamuwa da cutar coronavirus a cikin makonnin da suka gabata.
Gwamna Greg Abbott ya ba da sanarwar bala'i ga yankuna 32 da ke cikin guguwar, ciki har da Harris, Fort Bend, Galveston da Brazoria.
Ya ce: "Kowane hadari babban kalubale ne.
Wannan kalubale ya zama da rikitarwa kuma ya zama da tsanani, ganin cewa yana mamaye wani yanki wanda shine yankin da ya fi fuskantar kalubale a jihar don COVID-19. "
Fashewar farko ta faru ne da karfe 5 na yammacin ranar Asabar, mil 15 arewacin Port Mansfield, wanda ke da nisan mil 130 kudu da Corpus Christi.
Na biyu ya faru ne a gabashin Kennedy County.
Mutane fiye da 43,700 a kudancin Texas, ciki har da Corpus Christi, Harlingen da Brownsville, sun rasa wutar lantarki a ranar Asabar da yamma.
A birnin Corpus Christi, an kafa katangar da za a iya amfani da ita a lokacin da aka yi ruwa a kan tituna.
A wani sakon Twitter, Shugaba Donald Trump ya ce gwamnatinsa tana sa ido kan Hanna, tare da Hurricane Douglas, wanda ke kan hanyar zuwa Hawaii a Tekun Pacific.
Mazauniyar Sherry Boehme, wacce ke zaune a bakin rairayin bakin teku a Corpus Christi, ta ce guguwar da ke gabatowa ta kara ta damu a lokacin annobar.
Mutumin mai shekara 67 ya zauna a gida saboda rashin lafiya da ke tattare da ciwon huhu.
Ta ce: "A gare mu, kusan kamar mun yi wa juna biyu.
