Wani jami'in tsaro na FDNY ya ce 'yana da matukar dacewa' a hana wani fararen wuta yin aikin tsaro don haka masu dauke da tutar su kasance baki, a cewar wani sabon rahoto.
Lt. Daniel McWilliams mai aikin kashe gobara na fari ya shigar da kara da ikirarin nuna bambanci na launin fata bayan an cire shi daga rukunin da ke dauke da tutar a wani taron tunawa da ranar Nuwamba 2017 don girmama marayu membobin Vulcan Society, ƙungiyar 'yan uwan' yan wasan wuta na baƙar fata.
Kuma babban jami'in FDNY na bambancin da hada kai, lauya Cecilia Loving, ta kare wannan hukunci a wani shari'ar da aka yi a bangaren 'yancin bil adama na jihar New York, jaridar The New York Post ta ruwaito.
McWilliams na daya daga cikin 'yan kashe gobara uku na FDNY da aka gani a hoto mai ban mamaki yayin da suke ɗaga tutar Amurka a Ground Zero a cikin kwanaki bayan hare-haren 9/11.
A cewar korafin McWilliams, an zaba shi ta hanyar FDNY Ceremonial Unit don yin aiki a matsayin daya daga cikin masu dauke da tutar a cikin masu tsaron launi a bikin tunawa.
Kasancewa mai dauke da tutar a taron ya kasance 'daraja da gata' ga McWilliams, a cewar kararsa, CNN ta ruwaito.
Bayan ya isa taron, duk da haka, an hana McWilliams daga shiga cikin tsaron launi ta shugaban kungiyar Vulcan ta Regina Wilson saboda an ce ta nemi tsaron launi baki a taro.
Sai ta tambayi McWilliams - tsohon soja na shekara 29 na FDNY - ya 'taimaka a wani matsayi dabam.'
Daga cikin waɗannan ayyuka an ce ya nemi ya raka fararen hula kuma ya tara jami'an da suke saka riguna zuwa cikin rukuni daga taron.
McWilliams ya yi ikirarin cewa ya tambayi Wilson idan ta cire shi daga garken mai launi saboda ba shi da baƙar fata.
Ya ce ta tabbatar da hakan.
Wilson, tsohon soja na shekaru 21 na FDNY wanda kuma ya kasance wani ɓangare na ayyukan ceto na 9/11 , a bayyane ya maye gurbin McWilliams da ɗaya daga cikin membobin Vulcan Society.
McWilliams ya ce ya bar wurin tunawa 'don ya ceci kansa daga ƙarin kunya, kunya da kunya,' kamar yadda abokai da abokan aiki suka ji tattaunawarsu, jaridar New York Daily News ta ruwaito.
A lokacin da take ba da shaida a shari'ar, lauyan McWilliams, Keith Sullivan, ya tambayi Loving - wanda baƙar fata ne - 'To, neman mai tsaron baki gaba ɗaya ba nuna bambanci ba ne?'
'A'a, ba haka ba ne,' Loving ya ce, bisa ga New York Post.
Sullivan kuma ya tambayi Loving idan yana da kyau a nemi mai tsaro mai launin fata baki, wanda aka ambata cewa ta ce, 'Tabbas.'
A matsayin bayani, Loving ya ce yana da kyau a musanya fararen fata da baƙar fata don 'ɗaukaka ainihinmu da kabilunmu dabam-dabam don a sa a ji girman kai da kuma goyon bayan juna.'
McWilliams ya fara shigar da korafin nuna bambancin launin fata tare da FDNY a watan Janairun 2018.
Daga nan ya shigar da kara a kan Wilson, FDNY, birnin New York da kuma mutane marasa suna a watan Mayu 2019.
Bayan ya gabatar da korafinsa, Sullivan ya ce magoya bayan Wilson sun yi wa McWilliams rashawa kuma sun tsoratar da shi.
A wani lokaci, an ce ɗaya daga cikin magoya bayanta ya sa hannu a kan McWilliams kuma ya ce: 'Na ji labarinka, sun gaya mini za ka yi haka, yanzu ka san ni.'
A takaice, Sullivan ya rubuta cewa ƙin yarda da McWilliams daga matsayin masu tsaro na launin fata na taro 'yana da "ƙyama" kuma alamar daidaitaccen tsari a sashen kashe gobara.
Sullivan ya rubuta: "Idan kai baƙar fata ne kuma kana nuna bambanci ga fararen fata a wurin aiki, za ka sami bugun hannu a mafi kyau".
A cewar karar, Wilson ta samu 'sa'a daya na shawarwari' game da yadda ta bi da McWilliams.
