Mai tsara ayyukan Hukumar Shugaban kasa kan hana cutar Coronavirus, Sani Aliyu, ya bayyana cewa Najeriya ba za ta yarda wani baƙo ya shiga kasar ba, sai dai idan yana da hujja cewa an gwada shi a kasarsa kuma ba shi da cutar Coronavirus.
Aliyu ya yi wannan jawabin ne a taron manema labarai na Hukumar Shugaban kasa kan Rigakafin Coronavirus.
