Gwamnatin jihar Nijar ta yaba wa shugabancin Sultan yayin da ya kai shekaru 64.
Gwamnan jihar Nijar kuma Shugaban kungiyar gwamnonin Arewacin Tsakiya, Alhaji Abubakar Sani Bello, ya taya Sultan na Sokoto, Alhaji Muhammad Sa'ad Abubakar III murna da ranar haihuwarsa ta 64.
Sanarwar ranar haihuwar ta kasance a cikin sanarwar manema labarai da sakataren yada labarai na gwamnan, Mary Noel Berje, ya sanya hannu, yana taya janar mai ritaya murna da wannan taron.
A cewar sanarwar, Gwamna Abubakar Sani Bello ya bayyana Sultan na Najeriya a matsayin dan Najeriya na gaskiya wanda yake da gaskiya, mai kare hadin kai da zaman lafiya domin kasar ta ci gaba.
Gwamnan ya ce a matsayinsa na shugaban Jam'iyyar Jama'atu Nasrul Islam (JNI) da shugaban kasa na Majalisar Koli ta Najeriya don Harkokin Musulunci (NSCIA), da kuma shugaban Majalisar Tsakanin Addinai ta Najeriya (NIREC), ya taka muhimmiyar rawa wajen bunkasa wannan kasa.
Gwamnan a matsayinsa na shugaban kungiyar gwamnonin Arewacin Tsakiya, wadda ke da himma ga hadin kai da ci gaban yankin da kuma Najeriya baki daya, ya ce, "Zan iya bayyana cewa haihuwar mai girma Sultan a wannan yankin ba karamin rahama ba ne a gare mu, saboda aiki mai wuya da gaskiya a gudanar da shugabancin gargajiya kamar yadda ya dace ".
Taimakonku ga zaman lafiya da hadin kai yana nuna shugabancin mutanen Arewa. Za mu ci gaba da yin farin ciki da ku saboda yadda kuka ba da kanku da lokacinku ga mutanen ƙasar, saboda manufofinku masu kyau a gare su game da al'adu, addini da dabarun siyasa.
A matsayinka na cikakken shugaban kasa da kuma mai mulkin gargajiya, a tsawon shekaru ka horar da kanka don ganin cewa akwai yanayi mai kyau don zaman lafiya a kasar, ta hanyar bayyana hadin kai da zaman lafiya da ke inganta kyakkyawar fahimta tsakanin addinai da al'adu.
Ina rokon ku da sauran 'yan Najeriya da ku taya murna da wannan rana, kuma ina taya ku murna da inganta fahimtar mutane masu addini a ciki da wajen kasar da kuma kokarin da kuke yi a kasar nan.
Gwamnan ya yaba wa sarautarsa Sultan saboda yaƙar da yake yi da talauci, inganta kiwon lafiya da shirye-shirye don haɓaka ilimi a fannin fasaha da ƙwarewa a yankin, da kuma kasancewa mai mulkin al'adu na mutane.
Gwamnan ya yi addu'a cewa Allah ya ba Sultan lafiya mai kyau da kuma shekaru masu yawa na hidima mai amfani, da farin ciki da kuma ƙarfin don ci gaba da tushen zaman lafiya da ci gaba a dukan kasar.
Na kara da cewa ina fatan ranar haihuwar mai girma Sultan.
