Babu wani shiri na jana'izar da aka sanar.
Yayin da wasu 'yan iyalin suka yi farin ciki saboda iyawarsu na tuki, Maurice Petty ya sami lakabi "Shugaba" saboda iyawarsa na juya maɓallin.
Ya taimaka wa iyalinsa lashe tseren 198 da kuma gasar zakarun Turai bakwai a cikin jerin NASCAR, kuma ya kuma gina injuna da suka kai Hall of Famer Buddy Baker, Jim Paschal da Pete Hamilton zuwa nasara.
"Shugaba yana ɗaya daga cikin masu sana'a masu ƙwarewa a tarihin NASCAR", in ji shugaban da kuma babban jami'in Jim France.
"Ya ba da ikon da ya taimaka wa Ƙananan Kasuwanci su ƙayyade rinjaye a wasanni.
Duk da yake an san shi da aikinsa a ƙarƙashin ƙofar, Maurice ya taka rawa da yawa a bayan fage, yana yin abin da ya kamata don ya taimaka wajen kawo motocinsa zuwa hanyar nasara".
An haifi Maurice Petty a ranar 27 ga Maris, 1939, a Level Cross, North Carolina.
Ya bi mahaifinsa zuwa filin wasa yayin da yake girma, kuma ilimin injiniya ya taka muhimmiyar rawa a cikin Lee Petty lashe tsere 54 da kuma gasar cin kofin uku.
Ya fara farawa 26 a NASCAR Cup Series daga 1960-64, ya gama a cikin manyan 5 sau bakwai tare da 16 top-10 runs.
Amma da sauri ya yanke shawarar mai da hankali ga abin da ke faruwa a ƙarƙashin hular maimakon abin da ke faruwa a bayan motar, kuma hakan ya zama kyakkyawan mataki ga ɗan'uwansa, wanda zai dogara da injunansa a lokacin mulkinsa.
Richard, wanda zai dauki lakabi "The King", ya lashe gasarsa ta farko tare da The Chief lokacin da ya tuka Plymouth zuwa taken 1964.
Sun sake lashe lambar yabo a 1967, a 1970 da '71, kuma sun kara da uku kafin shekarun 1970 suka ƙare.
Takaddun bakwai sun kasance tare da Dale Earnhardt da Jimmie Johnson a mafi yawan tarihi.
"Maurice Petty na ɗaya daga cikin majagaba na gaskiya a NASCAR wanda ya taimaka wajen gina ɗaya daga cikin ƙungiyoyin NASCAR masu rinjaye a cikin Kamfanonin Kasuwanci", in ji darektan zartarwa na Hall of Fame Winston Kelley a cikin sanarwa.
"Ko da yake tarihin ya nuna cewa ya ci nasara 212 ne, amma Petty ya ci nasara fiye da 250 idan aka yi la'akari da dukan injunan da ya gina don abokan hamayyarsa.
Za a tuna da Chief har abada a matsayin ɗaya daga cikin mafi kyawun gina wutar lantarki a NASCAR".
Lee Petty ya mutu a shekara ta 2000 kuma matar Maurice Petty ta shekaru 52, Patricia, ta mutu a shekara ta 2014.
Har ila yau, shi ne kawun tsohon direba da mai watsa shirye-shirye Kyle Petty da Truck Series shugaban ma'aikatan Trent Owens.
"Duk da cewa mun rasa ɗaya daga cikin ainihin majagaba da jarumawan NASCAR, za a tuna da gadōn Maurice Petty da kuma ƙwaƙwalwar ajiyarsa, za a kiyaye shi, za a yi bikinsa kuma za a daraja shi", in ji Kelley.
Muna ta'azantar da iyalin Petty.
