Ma'aurata, waɗanda suka taka rawa a matsayin 'yan'uwa maza da mata a cikin jerin Netflix, an lura da su yayin da suke kallon gidan gona mai ban mamaki na Oxfordshire, wanda ke kan kasuwa don £ 1.2 miliyan.
Sun isa Range Rover da Laura, mai shekara 34, ta tuka, suna sanye da wando da kuma fararen tufafi, kuma wani mai sayar da dukiya ya tarye su ya kai su cikin gidan don su bincika ɗakin dakuna biyar.
A cikin White Lines, wanda aka yi fim a kaka ta baya, Laura ta taka rawa Zoe Walker, wanda ya gano ɓangaren Ibiza yayin da take binciken kisan gillar dan uwanta na DJ Axel, wanda Tom mai shekaru 28 ya buga.
Labarin dangantakarsu ya bayyana ne a farkon wannan watan, kasa da shekara guda bayan rushewar auren Laura na shekaru shida da Sam Claflin, wanda ya taka rawa a fina-finai na The Hunger Games.
Suna da ɗa, Pip mai shekara huɗu, da kuma 'yarsu Margot, biyu.
