Laura da Sam sun hadu a shekarar 2011 a wani sauraro kuma Sam, wanda kuma ya kasance a cikin Peaky Blinders, ya bayyana aurensu a shekarar 2013 a matsayin "sauƙin daya daga cikin manyan nasarorinsa".
Kafin White Lines, Laura ta bayyana a fim na farko na Inbetweeners da kuma wasan kwaikwayo na BBC na bara The Capture, yana taka rawa a matsayin lauya Hannah Roberts.
