Yarima Andrew yana shirin yaƙi da yiwuwar bayyana wannan makon na ƙarin zarge-zarge game da abokantakarsa da ɗan lalata Jeffrey Epstein da kuma zargin da ake yi da Ghislaine Maxwell.
Alkalin kotun Amurka Loretta Preska a makon da ya gabata ya ba da umarnin sakin takardun shari'a na sirri 80, da suka kai daruruwan shafuka, da suka shafi Maxwell da Epstein.
Buga wannan babban takarda zai zama babban abin takaici ga Maxwell, mai shekaru 58, saboda suna dauke da manyan sassan shaidar da ta bayar ga lauyoyi a shekarar 2016, gami da abin da tawagar lauyoyin ta ce "tambaya ce mai rikitarwa" game da rayuwarta ta jima'i.
Suna kuma iya matsa lamba a kan Yarima Andrew saboda ɗayan takardun sun haɗa da sadarwa tsakanin Maxwell da Epstein daga Janairu 2015, lokacin da Virginia Roberts, da ake zargi da zama bawan jima'i na mai saka hannun jari na Amurka, ta yi ikirarin a cikin takardun kotu cewa an tilasta mata yin jima'i da Yarima sau uku.
Andrew ya yi musun wannan da'awar a kai a kai.
Wata wasikar imel da aka fitar a shekarar 2015 da BBC ta bayyana a shekarar da ta gabata ta nuna cewa Andrew ya nemi taimakon Maxwell wajen magance da'awar Ms Roberts.
