MOPPAN ta sake maimaita fitar da Rahama Sadau.
Hukumar Kula da Fim din Kano ta dawo da ita, a cewar masu shirya fim.
Kungiyar masu sana'ar fim ta Kannywood ta Najeriya, wadda aka fi sani da MOPPAN, ta sake jaddada shawarar da ta dauka na korar daya daga cikin shahararrun 'yan fim din Hausa, Rahama Sadau bayan wani ya zargi Annabi Allah (SAW) sakamakon zargin da ta yi wa tauraruwar fim ta wallafa hotunanta a lokacin da yake yin tsokaci.
Za a tuna cewa, jarumar Rahama Sadau ta fuskanci zargi da kuma zargi daga al'ummomin musulmi da Hausa da kuma abokan aikinta da yawa saboda wallafa hoton da ta yi a Twitter, wani aiki da ya haifar da muhawara tsakanin mabiyan addinai daban-daban, bayan wani mai sharhi, wanda ake zargin ba musulmi ba ne, ya zargi Annabi Allah.
Wannan ya haifar da lakabi "Maganar Allah", kalmomin da actress ta fara amfani da su a kokarin da ta yi na bayyana rashin jin dadinta game da abubuwan da ta sha wahala daga wasu game da hoton, daga wadanda suka ce wannan ya saba wa koyarwar Musulunci, wanda ta bi.
Bayan mutumin da ake zargin ya yi ba'a game da Annabi ya kuma yi ta sukarsa, wannan ya jawo zargi har ma daga masu yin fina-finai a Arewacin Najeriya, don haka wannan ƙungiyar masu yin fina-finai ta fito ta nisantar da kanta daga actress.
A wata sanarwa da shugaban kasa, Dakta Ahmad Sarari ya fitar jiya, jami'in hulda da jama'a na kungiyar, Al-Amin Ciroma ya yi Allah wadai da ayyukan Rahama, yana mai cewa ita jaruma ce mai kunya a kungiyar, sai dai hukumar tsinkayar fina-finai ta jihar Kano (KSCB) karkashin jagorancin Ismail Na'abba Afakallahu ta dawo da ita ba zato ba tsammani.
Kungiyar ta tuna cewa tun daga shekarar 2016, an kori jarumar daga masana'antar saboda ta keta dokar kungiyar ta bayan ta fito a cikin wani bidiyo tare da wani Mai Waƙar da ake kira Classic inda suke rungumar juna.
Sanarwar ta ci gaba da cewa, "Kungiyar masu taka rawa a kungiyar masana'antar fim ta Arewacin Najeriya, MOPPAN, wanda aka fi sani da Kannywood, ta nuna rashin jin dadinta game da sanya hoton ta fitacciyar jarumar Rahama Sadau a shafukan sada zumunta", hoto wanda ke yaduwa a kafofin watsa labarai.
Hoton ya jawo zargi da yawa, kamar yadda hoton ya haifar da zargi ga Annabi Muhammad (salla Allahu alihi wa sallam) a Twitter da sauran dandamali na kafofin watsa labarun.
Wannan laifi ne mai ban mamaki kuma kungiyar ta MOPPAN ta la'anta shi.
Ana iya tunawa cewa kimanin shekaru hudu da suka gabata, a ranar 2 ga Oktoba, 2016, ƙungiyar ta kori Sadau daga masana'antar fim, amma bayan kimanin shekaru biyu KSCB ta ce ta yafe mata, duk da cewa Kano ita ce babbar cibiyar samar da fina-finai Hausa a duniya.
MOPPAN ta ce, "Shekaru biyu bayan fitarwa, Hukumar Kula da Fim din Jihar Kano (KSCB) ta hanyar shugabanta, Mallam Isma'il Na'Abba Afakkallah".
A ranar 8 ga Janairu, 2018, ƙungiyar ta yafe Rahama saboda duk wani zargin da ake yi da rashin adalci, kuma ta ba ta damar sake shiga Kannywood, wani mataki da reshen MOPPAN na jihar Kano ya kalubalanci a ranar 15 ga Janairu, 2018, a karkashin jagorancin shugaban reshen, Malam Kabiru Maikaba.
Sanarwar ta kara da cewa, "Ganin halin da ake ciki a yanzu, MOPPAN ta sake tabbatar da matsayinta na asali akan Rahama Sadau kuma ta yi kira ga dukkan kungiyoyin Kannywood da su bi wannan shawarar da kuma aiwatar da ita".
Daga nan ne kungiyar ta MOPPAN ta yi kira ga dukkan kwararrun da ke Kannywood da sauran al'ummar Hausa a gida da waje da su lura da cewa kungiyar ta riga ta nisanta kanta daga Rahama Sadau da duk wani laifi da ta yi yanzu ko kuma a nan gaba.
Mutane sun sake jin zafi cewa tauraron fim din ya ki cire sakonta da hotunansa har tsawon kwanaki.
Amma kuma bayan da abubuwa suka yi muni, ta cire hotunan kuma a jiya da yamma ta fito a shafukan sada zumunta tare da rubutu da bidiyo tana nisantar da kanta daga maganganun da ke zargi Annabi (SAW) da kuma mutumin da ya yi shi, ko da yake Sadau bai fito fili ba don amsa cewa ba daidai ba ne a buga hotunan a farkon wuri.
