Da wahala Manchester United ta samu nasarar shiga gasar zakarun Turai bayan ta lashe gasar Leicester City.
A wasan karshe, da kuma na 38 na kakar 2019 / 20, Manchester United ta ci nasara da gol biyu zuwa sifili a filin wasa na Kingpower na Leicester.
