Lokacin da wasan ya kusan ƙare a minti na 90, mai tsaron gidan Leicester City Kasper Schemiechel ya ba da kwallon ga mai tsaron gidan Manchester United Jesse Lingard, wanda ya yi amfani da damar don zira kwallo ta biyu nan take. Wannan ya sanya su a matsayi na huɗu kuma na ƙarshe a cikin ƙungiyoyin da za su wakilci ƙasar a gasar zakarun Turai ta shekara mai zuwa, bayan sun zira kwallaye 66.
