Yawan mutanen da suka kamu da cutar coronavirus ya ninka sau biyu a cikin makonni uku tun daga ranar 2 ga Yuli, lokacin da ƙasar ta ƙetare alamar miliyan shida.
A ranar Juma'a da ta gabata, adadin mutanen da ke kamuwa da cutar COVID ya kai maki miliyan 10.
Tun daga lokacin, an samu sabbin kamuwa da cutar kusan miliyan uku. Wannan ne rana ta huɗu a jere da adadin mutanen da suka kamu da cutar COVID-19 ya ƙaru da sama da 45,000.
A ranar Asabar, Maharashtra ta ba da rahoton sabbin mutane 9,251 da suka kamu da cutar COVID-19, wanda ya kawo jimlar jimlar jimlar a jihar zuwa 3,66,368 yayin da mutuwar ta karu da 257, ciki har da 116 a yankin Metropolitan na Mumbai (MMR), zuwa 13,389, in ji sashen kiwon lafiya na jihar.
An sallami marasa lafiya 7,227 a ranar, wanda ya kai adadin wadanda suka warke zuwa 2,07,194.
Kimanin marasa lafiya miliyan 8.85 sun warke zuwa yanzu; yawan warkewa ya kai kashi 63.91 cikin ɗari a safiyar yau.
Adadin masu kamuwa da cutar - kashi 11 cikin 100 na marasa lafiya da suka kamu da cutar coronavirus.
A farkon wannan makon, gwamnati ta ce tana da burin rage yawan kamuwa da cutar zuwa kashi 5.
Karnataka a ranar Asabar ta yi rikodin sabbin mutane sama da 5,000 da suka kamu da cutar coronavirus a rana ta uku a jere, inda jimillarta ta wuce 90,000.
Bangalore kadai ta ba da rahoton sabbin mutane 2,036 da suka kamu da cutar, wanda ya kai jimlarta zuwa 43,503.
Delhi ta inganta matsayinta a cikin adadin masu kamuwa da COVID-19 kuma a halin yanzu tana matsayi na takwas tsakanin jihohi da yankuna a cikin ƙasar, in ji Babban Minista Arvind Kejriwal a ranar Asabar.
A cikin mafi girma a cikin rana guda zuwa yanzu, Kerala a ranar Asabar ta ba da rahoton sabbin mutane 1,103 da suka kamu da COVID-19 wanda ya kawo adadin kamuwa da cutar zuwa 18,098, yayin da sama da mutane miliyan 1.5 ke karkashin lura.
Mutane 9,420 ne ke kan magani saboda cutar coronavirus.
An samu karin mutane 6,989 da suka kamu da cutar korona a Tamil Nadu a cikin awanni 24 da suka gabata, wanda kuma ya fi girma a cikin kwana daya, kamar yadda bayanan gwamnati suka nuna.
Mutane 89 ne suka mutu kuma 7,758 sun warke a cikin sa'o'i 24 da suka gabata.
Jimlar adadin masu kamuwa da cutar a jihar yanzu ya kai 2,06,737.
A ranar Asabar ne jihar Gujarat ta samu karuwar adadin masu kamuwa da cutar korona a rana guda da aka samu a cikin mutane 1,081, inda jimlar adadin mutane ya kai 54,712 yayin da mutane 22 suka mutu, ciki har da 11 a Surat, in ji sashen lafiya na jihar.
Babban Ministan Maharashtra, Uddhav Thackeray zai kaddamar da shirin bayar da jini a ranar 27 ga Yuli, bayan "Plasma Daan Sankalp Abhiyan" don tantancewar farko na marasa lafiya da suka warke daga COVID-19 a yankin Dharavi na Mumbai.
Kasar Indiya, ta uku da ta fi fama da cutar coronavirus a duniya bayan Amurka da Brazil, a hankali ta haɓaka ƙarfin gwajin COVID-19 kuma ta gudanar da gwaje-gwaje sama da miliyan 4.2 a rana, ma'aikatar lafiya ta Union ta ce a ranar Asabar, ta ba da crediting ga karuwar yawan dakunan gwaje-gwaje don nasarar.
A cewar kamfanin dillancin labarai na AFP, cutar ta kashe mutane sama da 6,33,000 a duniya tun lokacin da ta bayyana a kasar Sin a karshen shekarar da ta gabata, inda mutane sama da miliyan 15.5 suka kamu da cutar.
WHO ita ce jagoran yaki da cutar polio a Najeriya.
Faisal Shuaib, shugaban hukumar ci gaban kula da lafiya ta farko ta kasa (NPHCDA), ya ce Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ita ce jagora a yaki da cutar polio a Najeriya.
Shuaib ya yi wannan jawabin ne a lokacin da yake karbar wakilin WHO a Najeriya a ofishinsa a ranar Litinin.
Ya ce Najeriya za ta karbi takardar shaidar kawar da cutar polio a Afirka a watan Agusta daga Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya.
Wannan ya biyo bayan gamsuwa da Hukumar kawar da cutar polio a kasashen Afirka (ARCC) game da kokarin da gwamnati ke yi na nuna kawar da cutar polio a Afirka.
Za a tuna cewa a watan Agusta na shekarar 2016, cutar polio ta barke a Najeriya bayan shekaru uku babu barkewar cutar a kasar.
Cutar da ta barke a shekarar 2016 ta hana Najeriya da Afirka samun takardar shaidar kawar da cutar polio.
Bayan haka Shuaib ya ce gwamnati za ta ga an kawar da cututtukan da ke shafar kananan yara, musamman wadanda za a iya kawar da su ta hanyar rigakafi.
Mulombo ya yaba da kokarin da gwamnati ke yi na inganta fannin kiwon lafiya, musamman cibiyoyin kiwon lafiya na farko a kasar.
Saudiyya: Musulmai kalilan ne kawai za su yi aikin hajji.
A Saudiyya, masu aikin hajji suna shirin fara aikin hajji na wannan shekara, amma annobar Corona na iyakance yawan musulmai da ke son zuwa.
Mutane 10,000 ne kawai, ciki har da 'yan asalin ƙasar da kuma baƙi da ke zaune a ƙasar, za su iya yin aikin hajji, bisa ga sabon ƙa'ida mai tsauri da aka kafa don kiyaye wannan aikin addini.
Saudiyya na ɗaya daga cikin ƙasashen Gabas ta Tsakiya da suka fi yawan masu kamuwa da COVID-19, inda ta kashe mutane 2,733 daga cikin mutane sama da 260,000 da suka kamu da cutar.
Wannan shi ne karo na farko a tarihi da aka dauki matakan hana masu aikin hajji daga wasu sassan duniya shiga aikin hajji.
Ma'aikatar aikin hajji ta ce wajibi ne saboda tsoron yaduwar cutar Coronavirus.
Labarai na Yarima Harry: Abokin Duke na Sussex ya yi ta kai hari kan ikirarin fashewa a cikin sabon littafi
Mr Stott ya shaida wa Sky News cewa Yarima Harry da Meghan Markle cewa abun cikin littafin bai bambanta da na tabloids ba sai dai a cikin wani hardback.
Tsohon sojan ya bukaci a mai da hankali sosai ga abin da ma'aurata suke yi, har da aikin agaji.
Mista Stott ya ce: "Ina ganin abin da muke karantawa a nan bai bambanta da abin da muka karanta a jaridu ba amma yanzu yana kan takarda".
"Kana da halin marubucin, amma har yanzu ba a tabbatar da cewa ya fito ne daga gare su ba".
"Ina ganin wani irin hari ne kamar yadda jaridu suke ƙoƙarin tsananta musu".
"Na fahimci cewa suna cikin jama'a kuma mutane suna so su san abin da suke yi amma ina fata a mai da hankali ga nagarta da suke yi da kuma aikin sadaka maimakon sirri na sirri".
"Amma saboda su ne ba za su taɓa samun tsira daga hakan ba".
A ranar Asabar wani masanin tarihin sarauta ya kuma bayyana cewa Duke da Duchess na Sussex da ke tallafa wa Sarauniya sun "yi wa" sauran mambobin gidan sarauta.
Dr. Kate Williams ta shaida wa Sky News cewa dangin sarauta sun kasa amfani da ikon tauraron Yarima Harry da Meghan Markle.
Mai ba da bayani na sarauta ya kara da cewa dangin sarauta suna da tsananin matsayi amma ba za a iya jagorantar ko sarrafa sha'awar jama'a ba.
Ta ci gaba da cewa: "A gaskiya, duk abin da suka yi don su tallafa wa Sarauniya sau da yawa yakan sa sauran mambobin gidan sarauta su yi mamaki, kuma ana ganin hakan matsala ce".
"Suna da wannan babbar ikon taurari".
"Sun yi aure kaɗan fiye da 'yan'uwa da suke cikin matsayi ɗaya, Andrew ya yi aure mai girma, Anne ta yi aure mai girma".
"Sun yi karamin bikin aure amma har yanzu an yi magana game da bikin auren Harry da Meghan duk da cewa ya kasance karami amma har yanzu yana da girma kamar na William da Kate saboda akwai sha'awar duniya game da su".
Delhi Metro ta Fitar da Faya ta Farko a Mataki na 4
Jirgin karkashin kasa na Delhi ya kai wani muhimmin mataki a aikin na hudu yayin da ya fara aikinsa na farko a kan hanyar Janakpuri West-RK Ashram Marg da ake yi a yanzu, jami'ai sun ce a ranar Lahadi.
An jefa tashar a Keshopur a kan tsayi mai tsawo tsakanin Keshopur da Mukarba Chowk a ranar Asabar da daddare.
"Kamfanin jirgin kasa na Delhi Metro ya ɗauki wani muhimmin mataki a aikin gina shi na 4 yayin da aka fara kafa tashar farko ta wannan matakin na fadada Metro a kan gangaren Metro na Janakpuri West-RK Ashram Marg", in ji DMRC a cikin wata sanarwa.
An cimma wannan "babban ci gaban gini" duk da karancin ma'aikata da sauran kalubalen da ake fuskanta saboda annobar, jami'ai sun ce.
Matsakaicin tsayin matakai a wannan gangaren shine mita 10.
Duk da haka, tashoshin za su kasance mita 20 a Madhuban Chowk (ta hanyar wucewa tare da Layin 1) da kuma mita 25 a Haiderpur Badli Mor inda wannan layin zai haye Layin 2.
A Haiderpur Badli Mor, matakin viaduct zai kasance a mita 28, mafi girma a tarihin Metro na Delhi, in ji sanarwar.
A halin yanzu, mafi girma shine a Dhaula Kuan, inda layin 7 ya wuce a tsawo na 23.6m.
Ƙungiyoyi, a cikin gine-gine gine-gine sune gine-gine masu ɗaukar kaya masu tsaye waɗanda ke aiki a matsayin tallafi na tsakiya don ƙarshen gefen gefen biyu.
Suna samar da gine-ginen tallafi na tsaye wanda ke tsaye a kan manyan hanyoyin metro.
Tashoshin metro a yau suna da hanyoyi masu yawa a Delhi wanda manyan hanyoyin metro ke gudana.
Lambobin tashar jiragen ruwa yanzu suna da muhimmanci ga adiresoshin a fadin Delhi-NCR.
Hanya mai tsawon kilomita 28.92 ta Janakpuri West-R K Ahsram Marg wani tsawo ne na Magenta Line kuma zai zo da tashoshi 22.
Yayin da za a yi tsawo na kilomita 21.18 na wannan hanyar, kilomita 7.74 za su kasance a karkashin kasa.
An fara aikin gini a wannan sashe a watan Disamba na bara.
A ranar 17 ga Yuli, an fara aikin a ɓangaren karkashin kasa na wannan gangaren tare da fara aikin gina D Wall a tashar Metro ta Krishna Park Extension.
A ranar 24 ga Yuni, DMRC ta fara aikin casting na 'yan mata da za a shigar a kan babban sashin wannan gangaren.
A karkashin Mataki na 4, za a gina sabbin layukan metro na kilomita 61,679 a cikin ganguna daban-daban guda uku da suka hada da tashoshin metro 45.
Wadannan sabbin sassan za su samar da haɗin kai tsakanin sassan da suka riga sun yi aiki na Metro na Delhi.
Daga cikin wannan, kilomita 22.35 za su kasance a karkashin kasa yayin da za a kara yawan sauran.
Babban Kwamitin Harkokin Musulunci ya kalubalanci Shekau.
A wani taron manema labarai da Majalisar ta shirya a Kaduna dangane da barazanar da Shekau ta yi a wani bidiyo da ta fitar, lokaci ya yi da Shugaba Muhammadu Buhari ya farka don fuskantar wadannan kalubale.
Daya daga cikin manyan malaman addinin Islama na Najeriya, Sheikh Abdulwahab Abdullahi Mohammad, ya kalubalanci shugaban Boko Haram Abubakar Shekau a kan wani bidiyo da ya fitar inda ya bayyana cewa idan da gaske ya kasance mai karfin hali, to ya kamata ya fita daga ɓoye ya fuskanci jami'an tsaro.
Wannan ya zo ne a daidai lokacin da halin da ake ciki a Najeriya ke jawo hankali sosai, musamman ganin barazanar tsaro da ke fuskantar kasar a watan Fabrairu.
Najeriya na samun tallafin dala miliyan 890 don yaki da cututtuka daga 'Global Fund'.
Kungiyar "Global Fund" ta ba da dala miliyan 890 ga gwamnatin Najeriya don yaki da cututtuka a kasar.
Waɗannan cututtuka sun haɗa da AIDS, zazzabin cizon sauro da kuma tarin fuka.
Ministan lafiya Osagie Ehanire ya sanar da hakan a makon da ya gabata a Abuja.
Ehanire ya ce tallafin zai taimaka wajen inganta fannin kiwon lafiya na kasar, musamman a yaki da wadannan cututtuka da suka ci gaba a Najeriya.
Za a tuna cewa a watan Janairun 2020 Gwamnatin Tarayya ta sanar da cewa za ta dauki bashin dala miliyan 890 daga Asusun Kuɗi na Duniya don dakile yaduwar cutar a kasar.
Gwamnati ta ce za ta kashe kudaden don yaki da cutar AIDS, zazzabin cizon sauro da tarin fuka daga 2021 zuwa 2023.
Gwamnati ta ce don yaki da zazzabin cizon sauro za a sami mafi yawan kuɗin, wato, dala miliyan 417, na HIV da AIDS, dala miliyan 329, da na tarin fuka dala miliyan 143.
Ya kara da cewa gwamnati ta kafa matakan da za su taimaka mata wajen gudanar da kudade ta yadda ya kamata ba tare da kowa ya fadi cikin fasa ba.
An kashe jarumar Spencer Grammer a gaban gidan cin abinci na Manhattan
NEW YORK -- 'Yar wasan kwaikwayo Spencer Grammer ta ce tana kokarin kwantar da hankalin wani mutum mai tashin hankali lokacin da ya yanke ta a hannu kuma ya yi wa abokinta wuka a baya a ranar Juma'a a waje da gidan cin abinci na birnin New York.
Grammer, mai shekara 36, ta gaya wa US Weekly cewa ita da abokinta "sun yi abin da kowa zai yi a irin wannan yanayin" kuma suna "gwada su hana faɗa ta ƙaru" sa'ad da aka kai musu hari.
Grammer da abokinta mai shekara 32 suna cin abinci a teburin waje a The Black Ant a unguwar East Village ta Manhattan da misalin karfe 11:30 na dare.
A ranar Juma'a ne mutumin ya tashi ya nemi a ba shi abinci yayin da ake rufe gidan abinci.
'Yan sanda sun ce Grammer da abokinta sun ji rauni sa'ad da suka "ƙoƙari su warware jayayya tsakanin namiji da ba a san shi ba da kuma wasu masu ba da shawara a wurin", in ji 'yan sanda.
Mutumin ya gudu bayan ya raunata Grammer a hannun dama da abokinta a ƙananan baya tare da wani abu mai kaifi wanda ba a sani ba, 'yan sanda sun ce.
Babu wani kama.
Grammer, wanda ya ba da muryar Summer a "Rick da Morty" kuma ya yi aiki a cikin jerin ABC Family "Greek", 'yar 'yar Kelsey Grammer da actress Doreen Alderman.
Grammer ta ce ita da abokinta suna sa ran za su warke da sauri.
Ta ce babu wani cikin su da ya ji rauni a ciki.
A cikin sanarwar da ta bayar ga Us Weekly, Grammer ta gode wa masu ba da agaji na farko da ma'aikatan Asibitin Bellevue da suka kula da su kuma sun lura da "ƙoƙarin da ba a taɓa gaskatawa" da waɗannan ma'aikata suka yi da cutar coronavirus.
Grammer ya ce: "Mun yi farin ciki sosai da muka sami zarafin gode musu da kanmu.
Hukumar INEC za ta fara rajistar masu jefa kuri'a a shekarar 2021.
Hukumar zabe mai zaman kanta ta kasa INEC ta ce za ta fara rajistar masu jefa kuri'a a cikin watanni uku na farko na shekara mai zuwa.
Shugaban hukumar, Farfesa Mahmood Yakubu, ya sanar da hakan a wani taron manema labarai jim kadan bayan ya bayyana a gaban Kwamitin Majalisar Dattawa kan INEC don kare kasafin kudin hukumar na 2021.
Ya ce za su yi dogon lokaci suna yin rajistar masu jefa kuri'a inda za a dakatar da rajista da watanni shida kafin babban zaben 2023.
"Kwamishinanmu na da niyyar ci gaba da wannan aikin rajistar masu jefa kuri'a a farkon watanni uku na shekarar 2021, " in ji shi.
Da zarar mun koma aiki, za ta ci gaba da gudana har shekara daya da rabi, a takaice dai zai kasance kusan watanni shida kafin babban zaben 2023.
Ya ce, idan suka koma aiki, ba za su yi shi kawai mako-mako ko kowane wata ba, amma a maimakon haka, za a ci gaba da yin aikin, duk da haka, ba za su yi shi da sauri ba amma za su bi shi da hankali suna tattara kome.
Shugaban ya ce a halin yanzu INEC na fuskantar shari'o'i 1,700 da suka shafi kafin da bayan zaben 2019.
Ya ce, shari'o'in kotu suna cinye albarkatun su amma duk da haka suna ƙoƙarin bin matakan da doka ta tanada a cikin martani ga duk wani karar da aka shigar da su.
"Duk wanda ya je kotu ya hada da INEC a cikin shari'ar da aka shigar. Muna da shari'o'i kusan 1,700 kafin da bayan zaben 2019. Muna ci gaba da amfani da iyakokin albarkatunmu", in ji shi.
Yayin da yake kare kasafin kudin hukumar a gaban majalisar dattijai, Yakubu ya shaidawa 'yan majalisa cewa hukumar na shirin janye Naira biliyan 5.2 daga Naira biliyan 10 da ke cikin kasafin INEC don kammala kasafin 2020.
Ya ce biliyan 10 da suke magana a kai wani bangare ne na kudaden da hukumar ta ajiye tun lokacin da aka kaddamar da shi a shekarar 2010.
Ya ce wajibi ne a yi haka saboda karancin kasafin kudin shekarar 2020 da suka samu daga baya da kuma matsalolin da ta fuskanta, ciki har da cewa annobar Corona ta sa hukumar ba ta samu cikakken kasafin kudin shekarar 2020 kamar yadda aka tsara ba.
Game da 'yan Najeriya da ke zaune a kasashen waje, ya ce akwai doka da ta ba su damar kada kuri'a a lokacin zabe, ya kara da cewa da zarar dokar ta fara aiki za su iya samun damar kada kuri'a daga kasashen da suke zaune.
Wakilin majalisar wakilai Val Demings ya tattauna takarar mataimakin shugaban kasa, ya yi wa Trump ba'a don yafe masa
'Yar majalisa Val Demings (D-Fla.) ba ta jin kunya game da yarda ta ta yi aiki a matsayin mataimakin shugaban kasa a karkashin gwamnatin Joe Biden mai yiwuwa da kuma godiya ta gaskiya ga yin la'akari da wannan rawar.
A wata hira da aka yi da BlackPressUSA a matsayin wani ɓangare na jerin #FIYAH! live, ƙaunatacciyar memba na Congressional Black Caucus ta raba tarihinta da ɗabi'ar aiki da sadaukarwa da ta kawo ta wannan batu, ta bayyana, "Ku duka kun san tarihin na. Na girma a matsayin 'yar uwargida da mai kula da gida a Jacksonville, Florida".
Demings ya yi aiki a matsayin daya daga cikin Manajan Gidajen Majalisar Dokoki guda bakwai a lokacin shari'ar Janairu na Shugaba Donald Trump a Majalisar Dattijai.
Ko da kuwa Majalisar Dattawa ta tabbatar da cewa ba shi da laifi, tarihi zai tabbatar da cewa shi ne kwamandan na hudu da aka yi masa tuhuma.
Tsohon Manajan Kotun Majalisar, ya amsa a wata hira da NPR a watan Fabrairu daga ofishinta na Capitol Hill, "Shin ya cancanci shi? Kowace rana ya cancanci shi".
Bugu da ƙari, yayin da hukuncin ya kasance abin takaici, 'yan Democrat suna da alhakin ci gaba da shari'ar ba tare da la'akari da sakamakon ba.
A lokacin hirar, Demings ta bayyana a fili cewa ta yi jayayya da Trump don sauya hukuncin da aka yanke wa Roger Stone, wanda aka yanke masa hukuncin yin karya ga Majalisa (a tsakanin sauran laifuffuka) da kuma gafarta wa wasu masu laifi da aka yanke musu hukuncin aikata irin wannan laifi, yana mai cewa, "Girman gafarta wa abokanka, waɗanda suka yi ƙarya kuma suka yaudare don rufe laifuffukanka".
Demings ya jagoranci jerin abokan aikin Biden na iyawar da ke gudana tare da Shugaban CBC Karen Bass (D-Calif.), Tsohon Wakilin Jihar Georgia Stacey Abrams, Sanata Kamala Harris (D-Calif.) da Tammy Duckworth (D-Illinois), Magajin garin Atlanta Keisha Lance Bottoms, Tsohon Jakadan Amurka Susan Rice da wasu 'yan' yan.
Ta lura, duk da haka, cewa mutum ɗaya ne kawai zai yanke shawarar wanda zai tsaya takara tare da Joe Biden a wannan kaka.
"Wannan Joe Biden ne".
Sai ta ɗaga hannu ta yi dariya, ta yi wa masu kallon bidiyon magana, ta ce, "Idan kuna son yin kira, ku yi".
Babu shakka cewa ko da wane irin siyasa ne mutum yake da ita, tarihi zai dubi wannan lokaci a matsayin lokaci na juyin halitta a siyasar Amurka da kuma ra'ayoyinta.
Ba a rasa wannan gaskiyar ba ga Demings.
Ta lura cewa samun wasu mata a cikin la'akari don takarar mataimakin shugaban kasa yana wakiltar damar da za a karya abin da ya rage daga rufin gilashi - musamman idan ya zo ga matan Afirka na Amurka.
Ta ce: "Wannan shi ne ainihin damar da na yi aiki tuƙuru a dukan rayuwata don in samar wa yara maza da mata da aka gaya musu cewa ba su da launi, ba su da kuɗi, ko kuma ba su da jinsi", in ji ta.
'Yar majalisa ta yi alkawarin tabbatar da cewa Kwamitin Jam'iyyar Democrat da yakin neman zaben Biden suna tallatawa da kuma aiki tare da Black Press na Amurka don samun mafi yawan mutane su jefa kuri'a.
"Zan kira [Shugaban DNC] Tom Perez kuma zan sanya wannan a saman jerin na", Demings ya yi alkawari.
Ta amince ya kamata a yi shi yanzu, maimakon a lokacin yakin neman zabe.
Da yake amsawa ga tsohuwar sakataren harkokin wajen Hillary Clinton ta bayar da shawarar cewa Trump na iya ki barin fadar White House idan aka doke shi, da kuma wani edita dabam wanda ya bayyana cewa shugaban yana neman ya gafarta wa kansa, Demings ya zama mai rai, "Ko da ya ba da shawarar ya gafarta wa kansa ya sa na yi rashin lafiya a ciki".
"Amma wane ne zai yi hakan banda Trump?
Ina ganin yana ƙin aikin.
Ba aikin da ya kamata a bar ka ka karya doka kuma ka yi watsi da Tsarin Mulki ba.
Ina ganin yana ƙin aikin, amma yana ƙin rasa.
Na ga shugaban kasa ba ya son barin fadar White House, amma muna da hanyar da za mu magance hakan, kuma idan hakan ta faru, ina so in kasance cikin tawagar da ke sa hakan ya faru".
Kotun Duniya ta fara binciken zanga-zangar EndSARS.
Kotun kasa da kasa da ke hukunta wadanda suka aikata laifuka masu tsanani, wato Kotun Laifuka ta Duniya (ICC), ta fara gudanar da bincike na farko dangane da tashin hankali da ya barke a kan zanga-zangar neman kawo karshen sashin 'yan sanda, #EndSARS, da ya faru a fadin Najeriya.
Ofishin mai gabatar da kara na ICC ya shaida a cikin wata sanarwa da ya saki yana cewa ya karbi bayanai game da zargin aikata laifuka a lokacin zanga-zangar da suka juya zuwa tashin hankali da lalata lalata gwamnati da dukiya da dukiya ta jama'a.
Masu zanga-zangar sun shafe makonni da dama a titunan biranen kasar suna zanga-zangar adawa da cin zarafin da jami'an 'yan sanda ke yi.
Kimanin fararen hula 51 da 'yan sanda 11 da sojoji bakwai ne suka mutu, a cewar shugaban Najeriya Muhammadu Buhari lokacin da ya ba da shawarar ga al'ummar duniya yadda za a shawo kan matsalar.
Daga bangarenta kuma kungiyar kare hakkin bil adama, Amnesty International, ta ce jami'an tsaro sun bude wuta a kan masu zanga-zangar, inda suka kashe da kuma jikkata mutane da dama.
Sojoji da 'yan sanda sun musanta zargin da Amnesty International ta yi, amma Kotun ta ICC ta ce za ta bayyana sakamakon binciken ta na farko ga jama'a.
Taron nuna rashin amincewa na EndSARS, wanda ya fara ne a Legas da Abuja, ya kuma yada zuwa wasu jihohin kasar, kafin ya karu zuwa tashin hankali, wanda ya haifar da asarar rayuka da dukiya a cikin al'ummomin su.
Wasu da ake zargi da yin laifi sun yi amfani da zanga-zangar don lalata gine-ginen gwamnati da na wasu 'yan siyasa, musamman a jihar Legas, a yankin kudu maso yammacin kasar.
Hukumomi sun tura 'yan sanda masu yaki da tarzoma don dakile lamarin, amma tashin hankali ya ci gaba da ƙaruwa sakamakon kisan 'yan adawa a Lekki.
Masu zanga-zangar sun zargi jami'an tsaro da bude musu wuta a Lekki, jihar Legas, wanda shine cibiyar da ake gudanar da zanga-zangar, zanga-zangar da ta sa mutane da yawa suka ji rauni.
Wasu sun yi imanin cewa harbi a kan masu zanga-zangar ya sa yanayin ya tabarbare, musamman a jihar Legas.
