Corona: Mutane 137 sun kamu da cutar Corona a Najeriya a ranar Talata.
Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka ta Kasa (NCDC) ta sanar da karin mutane 137 da suka kamu da cutar coronavirus a Najeriya a ranar Talata.
Kididdiga da hukumar kula da lafiyar jama'a ta NCDC ta fitar a ranar Talata ta nuna cewa jihar Legas tana da karin mutane 60, Abia-21, FCT-18, Rivers-13, Kaduna-5, Oyo-4, Edo-3, Delta-2, Imo-2, Kano-2, Ogun-2, Bauchi-1, Gombe-1, Nasarawa-1 Niger-1 da Osun-1.
Ya zuwa yanzu mutane 63,173 ne suka kamu da cutar a Najeriya, 59,634 sun warke, kuma 1,151 sun mutu.
Bayan haka, wasu mutane 2,375 suka kamu da cutar a Najeriya.
Jihar Legas har yanzu tana da mafi yawan wadanda suka kamu da cutar, tare da mutane 21,398 da suka kamu da cutar, FCT -6,142, Oyo -3,456, Edo -2,669, Delta -1,816, Rivers 2,844, Kano -1,749, Ogun -2,053, Kaduna -2,663, Katsina -953, Ondo -1,669, Borno -745, Gombe -938, Bauchi -713, Ebonyi -1,049, Plateau -3,652, Enugu -1,314, Abia -898, Zamfara -619, Jigawa - 325, Kwara -1,069, Bayelsa -413, Nasarawa -483, Osun -930, Sokoto -165, Niger -277, Akwa Ibom -295, Benue -493, Adamawa -252, Anambra -277, Kebbi -93, Zamfara -79, Yobe -79, Ekiti -335.
Yana yiwuwa mutum da ya kamu da cutar Corona zai sami matsalar rashin lafiyar hankali.
Likitoci a Jami'ar UCL a Burtaniya sun bayyana cewa yana yiwuwa mutum wanda ya kamu da cutar Corona zai iya samun matsalolin lafiyar hankali.
Shugaban wannan bincike kuma jami'in UCL Ross Paterson ya sanar da cewa ya zama dole a yi ƙarin bincike don sanin yadda za a iya ganin rashin lafiyar da cutar za ta iya haifar wa mutum.
Cutar Corona ita ce ɗaya daga cikin ƙwayoyin cuta waɗanda ke sa mutum ya kamu da sanyi, wanda idan ya yi tsanani, zai iya haifar da wahala daga wahalar numfashi, wanda ake kira Middle East Respiratory Syndrome (MERS-CoV), da kuma mummunan cuta wanda zai iya toshe makogwaro.
Amma Corona Virus sabon cuta ne wanda ba a taba gano shi a jikin mutum ba.
Alamun kamuwa da cuta sun haɗa da matsalolin hanyoyin numfashi a cikin wuya wato rashin numfashi, zazzabi mai yawa, tari mai tsanani, da kuma ciwon wuya.
Idan kuma cutar ta yi tsanani, za ta iya sa mutum ya yi rashin numfashi, kuma ya yi fama da ciwon huhu.
Akwai wasu matakan gaggawa da za su taimaka wajen kauce wa wannan kamuwa da cuta, kamar wanke hannuwan da yawa da sabulu da ruwa, da kuma rufe hanci da baki a duk lokacin da kake yin sneezing.
Ka kuma tsabtace nama da qwai kuma ka dafa su sosai kafin ka ci.
Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ta ce a koyaushe a guji yin cuɗanya da waɗanda suke nuna alamun rashin lafiya, musamman waɗanda aka ambata a sama, kuma a je asibiti nan da nan don a yi musu magani idan ba su da lafiya.
