An yi safarar kwayoyin cutar daga Myanmar, wanda kudinsa ya kai kimanin Rs 1.55 crore a kasuwar kasar: 'Yan sanda
An kama wani mutum da dansa da nauyin heroin na kilo 1.9 a gundumar Hnahthial ta Mizoram kusa da iyakar Myanmar, 'yan sanda sun ce a ranar Lahadi.
Sun ce an yi safarar kwayoyin cutar ne daga Myanmar, wanda kudinsa ya kai kimanin Rs 1.55 crore a kasuwar yankin.
An kama Duhkima (62) da dansa Remthangpuia (33) tare da miyagun ƙwayoyi a daren Juma'a daga ƙauyen Ngharchhip, in ji 'yan sanda.
Sun kuma sauke kimanin gram 280 na heroin, mai darajar Rs 15 lakh, yayin da suke yin iyo a fadin kogi yayin da suke kokarin tserewa daga 'yan sanda, jami'an sun ce.
A cewar 'yan sanda, an yi imanin cewa wannan ne babban safarar heroin a jihar.
An zargi wadanda ake zargi da sassan da suka dace na Dokar Magunguna da Magungunan Psychotropic (NDPS) na shekarar 1985.
Ko da yake an rufe iyakokin jihohi da na Myanmar a sakamakon barkewar cutar coronavirus, safarar kwayoyi da sauran kayayyakin kwayar cutar ta ci gaba ba tare da raguwa ba, majiyoyin 'yan sanda sun ce.
Kungiyar Assam Rifles ta kama motocin da aka kwashe da kayan kwalliya masu nauyin Rs 4 crore daga Myanmar, sun ce.
Mick Fleetwood ya girmama Peter Green: 'Waƙarsa za ta ci gaba da rayuwa'
Mick Fleetwood ya yi wa Peter Green, wanda ya kafa kungiyar Fleetwood Mac, wanda ya mutu a yau yana da shekaru 73.
Green ya kasance memba na farko na ƙungiyar dutse mai ban mamaki, tare da Mick da aka ambata a sama, da kuma Jeremy Spencer.
Duk da barin ƙungiyar a shekara ta 1970 kafin manyan nasarorin su tare da kundin kamar Rumours, Mick ya girmama tsohon abokin ƙungiyarsa, yana tabbatar da magoya baya cewa "waƙarsa za ta ci gaba da rayuwa".
Fleetwood ya gaya wa PA: "A gare ni, da kuma kowane memba na Fleetwood Mac na baya da na yanzu, rasa Peter Green abu ne mai ban mamaki.
"Peter ne ya kafa ƙungiyar Fleetwood Mac tare da ni, John McVie, da kuma Jeremy Spencer.
Babu wanda ya taɓa shiga cikin rukunin Fleetwood Mac ba tare da girmama Peter Green da baiwarsa ba, kuma ga gaskiyar cewa kiɗa ya kamata ya haskaka da haske kuma koyaushe a ba da shi da sha'awar rashin jituwa. "
Wani ɗan shekara 73 da ya yi suna ya ce: "Peter, zan yi na'am da kai sosai, amma ka daina yin waƙa.
Na gode maka da ka gayyace ni in zama mai buga maka dukan waɗannan shekarun da suka wuce.
Mun yi kyau, kuma wannan waƙa ta sa mutane da yawa su ji daɗin waƙar.
"Allah ya yi sauri zuwa gare ku, aboki na mafi ƙaunataccena... ƙauna Mick Fleetwood".
Da yake tabbatar da mutuwar Green, wata sanarwa daga lauyoyin Swan Turton ta ce: "Da baƙin ciki mai girma ne iyalan Peter Green suka sanar da mutuwarsa a wannan karshen mako, cikin kwanciyar hankali a cikin barci.
"Za a ba da ƙarin bayani a cikin kwanaki masu zuwa".
Green ya tsira da 'yarsa, Rosebud Samuels-Greenbaum, wanda ta raba tare da tsohuwar matar Jane Samuels.
Green ya kafa Fleetwood Mac tare da abokan aiki Mick Fleetwood da Jeremy Spencer, tare da ƙungiyar da aka kira Fleetwood Mac na Peter Green wanda Jeremy Spencer ya gabatar.
Duk da haka, mawaƙa-mai rubutun waƙoƙi zai bar ƙungiyar a 1970, bayan kundin waƙoƙi huɗu.
Fleetwood Mac zai ci gaba da samun yabo mai girma da kuma shahararren duniya tare da ƙarin haɗin gwiwa ciki har da Lindsey Buckingham da Stevie Nicks a kan kundin tarihi ciki har da Rumours da Tusk.
